name: Cat way Domino
description:
Catway is a puzzle game based on Dominoes pieces. Set the right pieces in the path to allow the cat reaches the target alive.

Features

  • 70 challenge levels.
  • Discover a new way to play Domino.
  • Set the best pieces to remove less lives as possible from the cat.
  • Each piece removes the difference between values from the cat lives.
  • Minimalist Design.
  • Relaxing music.

Choose your pieces and set it on board
